\par "Tesad\'fcf" inanc\'fd, canl\'fdl\'fd\'f0\'fdn basit san\'fdld\'fd\'f0\'fd 19. y\'fczy\'fdlda do\'f0mu\'fe, baz\'fd ideolojik nedenlerle de 20. y\'fczy\'fdla kadar zorla ta\'fe\'fdnm\'fd\'fet\'fdr. Ama art\'fdk bilim d\'fcnyas\'fd bu iddian\'fdn sa\'e7mal
